title: Positive Dissatisfaction
itunes:title: Positive Dissatisfaction
description:
Episode 156 - Success and personal growth are hard. One of the main reasons is because it forces us to look at the future we want which in most cases makes us unhappy with where we currently are. In this episode I dive into how to be happy with where you are while still fighting to get to where you want to be.
